    dependents varchar(5), -- yes or no

    payment_method varchar(30),
    monthly_charges decimal(10,2),
    total_charges decimal(10,2),
    churn varchar(5) -- yes or no
);

paragraphs.title: Spread of charge amounts
paragraphs.text:
%splicemachine
select t.spread as charge_range, count(*) from(
select customer_id,
    case when monthly_charges >= 0 and monthly_charges < 25 then '0-24'
    when monthly_charges >= 25 and monthly_charges < 50 then '25-49'
    when monthly_charges >= 50 and monthly_charges < 75 then '50-74'
    when monthly_charges >= 75 and monthly_charges < 100 then '75-99'
    else '>100' end as spread from customer_churn.telco_customer_churn) t
group by t.spread
order by t.spread

    new_string_cols.append(stringCol+ "_INDEXED")

        new_string_cols[-1] = new_string_cols[-1] + "_ENCODED" # replace the stringindexer with the one hot encoder columnn 
        transformations.append(onehot) 

new_string_cols.remove('label_INDEXED')

transformations.append(VectorAssembler(inputCols=new_string_cols, outputCol='features'))
